Manchester United have placed security guards at Angel di Maria’s house after an attempted break-in on Saturday night.

United’s Argentinean star was left shaken by an attempted robbery as he watched TV with his wife and young daughter in Cheshire.

Now United have given the record signing round the clock security from members of their own CES security group. 

